Usage: getHierMode [-help] [-addAntennaCell] [-optStage] [-quiet] [-nonDefault]

-help                                     # Prints out the command usage
-addAntennaCell                           # add antenna diode to interface load
                                          # (bool, default=false)
-optStage                                 # Turn on default settings for
                                          # hierarchical flows at different
                                          # optimization stage.
                                          # (enums={preCTS postCTS unset}, default=unset)
-quiet                                    # Displays the current settings in Tcl list format only
-nonDefault                               # Displays the current settings which are not default settings